summary: This is an email from the FBI's Enterprise Vetting Center requesting a name check for an individual associated with Infragard. The request is expedited and seeks information on the subject's character, reliability, and trustworthiness, referencing a case number (50D-NY-3027571).

events.title: Expedited name check request

keyFacts: The FBI's Enterprise Vetting Center is processing an expedited name check for an Infragard member.
The request is treated with the same urgency as an EC lead in Sentinel due to time constraints from a partner's request.
The subject of the name check may be located in or associated with case number 50D-NY-3027571.
The email is classified as UNCLASSIFIED//FOUO (For Official Use Only) and marked as transitory.
The request seeks information bearing on the subject's character, reliability, and trustworthiness.
